Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:06.06,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You're late, even though you're the one who called us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.48,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I've received orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:12.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,We're to assassinate the guru again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.07,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:18.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's more. About the fate of the woman who was captured...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.08,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is she to be disposed of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.36,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,We can't afford to fail this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.08,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.32,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Tomorrow. Sixteen hundred hours at the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.58,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Yeah, that isn't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.82,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hold it, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:39.35,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I've received orders as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.35,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:43.98,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,To be precise, you and I have received orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.54,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,If Huang cannot kill the captive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.61,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,we're to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.27,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,The west side is completely open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:17.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Got it. Your cue will be when the alarm starts to sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:58.62,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.23,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's with that expression? Did they inject truth serum into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:11.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You better not have forgotten who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.19,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Have they already noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.65,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Where's the guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.62,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Tell us where she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:31.65,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The guru isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:37.09,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,On a slope two hundred meters north of here lies a deserted village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.51,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,She's in one of those houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.80,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It'll be hard to miss since she'll be surrounded by guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.43,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:50.56,DTB-Default,Guard A,0,0,0,,The guru's tired. Make it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.94,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I know. I just came to confirm whether she'll secure more dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.97,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Let's go. We're going to act as decoys until Hei reaches the guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.32,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.27,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.07,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,If you retreat without saying a word, I won't go after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:41.28,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,If you came to kill Arma, I won't be able to turn a blind eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.45,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,They're pretty tough for a religious cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:05.62,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm not allowed to kill you without Amber's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:08.66,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,She wants to recruit you as a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.69,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Quite an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.27,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Why don't you accompany me without making a scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:15.28,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:32.33,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Come in. I know you're out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:36.85,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,It isn't a trap. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.20,DTB-Default,Subordinate,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to go after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.27,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.59,DTB-Default,Subordinate,0,0,0,,Isn't he after the guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.81,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Transporting the dolls is our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.81,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I'll find another route to secure the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:55.30,DTB-Default,Subordinate,0,0,0,,Did the negotiations with the guru fall apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.34,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Fall apart? She's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.91,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,She no longer serves any purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:05.42,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Two more... What a troublesome remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.35,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,My cholesterol level is going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:15.19,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You're a frightening woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.81,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You sent a chill down my spine a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.17,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It reminded me of that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:25.45,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You became close to me, as planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:29.27,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,in order to acquire information that Isozaki and I had found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.99,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.68,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Are you willing to let this relationship drag on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.13,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.45,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's not like I have any relatives who would bug me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:47.26,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say? Were you thinking about tying the knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:48.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I-Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:53.77,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I thought so. You're not the type of person who'd do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.48,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's not an issue about what kind of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.46,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I get it. You're worried about a conflict of interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.38,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:09.47,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You know... I don't have a very good-looking face or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:13.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,and I'm barely home when I'm after a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:14.85,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.04,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,If you're okay with me, Kiyopii,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.65,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I'd be... really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.11,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.51,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.96,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen you drunk, Kiyopii.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,No, I'm not drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.30,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Hey! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.98,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm always careful. Come on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.36,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It looks like I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.23,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Did I make you happy enough to get drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.46,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Idiot. I'm not saying this because I'm drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,even though I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.40,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.99,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.38,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Kiyopii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.09,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:36.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I wondered why you would ask me about the photo Isozaki and I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.06,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I can't recall anything that happened after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.99,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,but it looks like I told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:48.52,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You disappeared from my sight a few days after that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Why did you kill Isozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:57.57,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Isozaki's wife had her memory erased by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.28,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,All of her memories about Isozaki vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:03.60,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Isozaki was erased twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.13,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Once from this world, and once from the memories of the woman he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.22,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:14.72,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The man called Isozaki hid his actual identity from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.43,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:20.14,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The group of illegal aliens you were going after
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.71,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,consisted of the cult's founding members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:27.48,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Isozaki was secretly connected to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.99,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.34,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,The photo you found that day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.26,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,was of Arma's actual appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.80,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:44.75,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,You're the contractor from that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.51,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Isozaki was determined to destroy the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.78,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,He pretended to report it to his superiors, but he actually hid the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.04,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:09:00.46,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,At that time, it was unknown whether it was you or Isozaki who was the spy for the cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.39,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.81,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Is that why you approached me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.97,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is that your true appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.87,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:17.53,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:21.56,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,My remuneration is aging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.81,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Aging?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.44,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Every time I use my ability to transform, I grow older.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:29.54,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,It looks like I've run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:34.57,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Twenty Dreaming Shallow, Uninebriated... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.38,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.11,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,We'll wait one hour for Hei to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.90,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What if he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.07,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'll go back to the cult grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.60,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,after I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.39,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's one more thing I have to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:04.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Why weren't my memories erased?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.23,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:10.71,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.20,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Help... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.84,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Hey, Shihoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.39,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.08,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:28.48,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Why do you let the syndicate exploit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:32.22,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,I suppose they wouldn't leave you alone, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.44,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,You could call it the contractor's karma, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.45,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,You disregard social and moral standards
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:44.61,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,and show no remorse for using your abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.70,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,which enables you to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:51.66,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,It creates a convenient image of a machine meant to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:55.17,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,which is a stereotype that humans are comfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:59.51,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You make it sound as if contractors aren't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:03.02,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,That's what they want you to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:11.02,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,In order to liberate contractors from this karma, I have chosen religion as my foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:16.47,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,In the beginning, it was more like an expedient, a cover of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:21.45,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,However, I still believe I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:26.26,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Do you know what differentiates contractors from humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.29,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Contractors don't have a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.79,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:39.41,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Contractors have no sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:42.10,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Whether they're committed by contractors or by people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.00,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,crimes will never cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:48.71,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,There's a significant difference between those who possess abilities and those who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:51.77,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Think of that as a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:58.51,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Even if you don't have special abilities, you have the power to take the life of another with a gun or knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:04.27,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,The most significant difference between humans and contractors is in their mental composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.41,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,In other words, their rational discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:11.29,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,In a human society, ideas like compassion and consensus are afterthoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:16.24,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,to the pursuit of profit, the driving force behind success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:23.74,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Contractors may be the deus ex machina in the race to a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Contractors can't see dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.88,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:34.36,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,The ideal relationship between contractors and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:41.10,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Then again, I've used my powers to kill people in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:45.93,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Until that happened, I had second thoughts about using it because of my overwhelming remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:52.27,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,However, ever since then, I've decided to use my abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.27,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:05.68,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Repeated use of my powers will result in repeated fulfillment of my remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.77,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,I thought I could atone for my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:14.27,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange for a contractor to mention something like atonement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:19.70,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,It looks like the time has come to make my final remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:26.70,DTB-Default,Arma,0,0,0,,I'll finally be liberated from this karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.51,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Isn't it an ironic remuneration?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:40.38,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I regain my human conscience for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:47.83,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That's why I understand what I'm doing... and how horrifying it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.01,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's as if this was my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.38,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.50,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:08.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You're not going to deceive me! I'm sick of this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.14,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.26,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,A part of me feels somewhat relieved,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:18.12,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,since I normally don't have a sensation of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:23.01,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Contractors have memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.63,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,but it's not quite the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:29.32,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's my own memory, but it feels distant for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.72,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That night was different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.34,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That night, when you said you wanted to be with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.17,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,my memories were of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.66,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,the chirping of insects, the sound of the flowing river,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.96,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,the dry, chilly wind of that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.64,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,the shimmering stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:54.10,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I forgot to play my role during that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.79,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I was simply happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.52,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's a happy, yet cruel memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:05.87,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,but it's the only one I have of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:11.59,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I was afraid that the memories of our time together would disappear from you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:16.10,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Having your memory erased isn't much different from being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.10,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I didn't want to become like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.13,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,So it was you, Shihoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.98,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,who arranged for the preservation of my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.96,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Come on. Aren't you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:38.07,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You seem to be acquainted with that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.27,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.96,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is she the reason you made that mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.79,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I told you that it doesn't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.04,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.70,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.82,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What an ugly scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.46,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shoot both of us with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.70,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:10.65,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:14.18,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You have a compassionate side to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.66,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.30,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you're saying, Huang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.27,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She's a contractor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.99,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I do have a soft spot, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:25.96,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.72,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei, what are you doing? Don't tell me you're going to let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.64,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You're out of your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.25,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,This isn't the same situation as with the doll from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.23,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's kill or be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.73,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:52.01,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What are we, the dogs of the syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.92,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Don't think about doing anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:56.39,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He's not the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:17:00.40,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,This isn't about contractors or humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.79,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,How many times have we been saved by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.90,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Huang, speak with the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.88,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,There's no fear about a leak of information, now that she's been freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:11.93,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,There's no need to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.59,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,This is a penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.71,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:18.18,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,We messed up the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.43,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The syndicate knew about my relationship with Shihoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.63,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,They issued the order with that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.34,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,In that case, run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.50,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.96,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,D-Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.60,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's no way I could run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.92,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The syndicate will go after you guys as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.39,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,That's none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.41,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I-I don't know anything about this. I didn't hear a thing, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.25,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,There's no way we could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.57,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I'm just a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:54.66,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,If I regain my emotions as a contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:18:00.48,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's too bad. I've had a long history with contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:05.06,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell the difference between me and them at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.61,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.44,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hei's inside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:26.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Wait for me there until the arrangements have been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:36.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.45,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.18,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,It's a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:50.65,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to have the mindset of a contractor now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.44,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,but I feel so... happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.88,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.35,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Aren't contractors human as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.76,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,You're right. It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.78,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,That's all I needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,A boat will arrive in thirty minutes at the far end of the pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.96,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.48,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Kiyopii.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:37.22,DTB-Default,Driver,0,0,0,,I didn't do it! She jumped in front of the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.65,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.03,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:43.83,DTB-Default,Shihoko,0,0,0,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.23,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Shihoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:20:00.20,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She knew that the syndicate had already taken action.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.55,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That isn't true, is it, Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:07.08,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Contractors don't think about suicide, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, Shihoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.35,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.58,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.67,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.87,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you? You were staring into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.52,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I was just dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.46,DTB-Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.96,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'd like to be, if it was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:44.17,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,A conspiracy dwells deep beneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.98,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,A black dragon yearns to wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.62,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,No answers are to be found in the allegations,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.34,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,and the road to the terminal lies hidden in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:58.22,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The strings that cross paths are unexpectedly tangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.47,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Destiny is disturbed and blood spills.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.26,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The puppet is controlled, unbeknownst to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.26,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Twenty-One City Under Crackdown, Moist with Tears... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.32,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,and the man disappears.